title: Unexpected panic at 'explicit panic', src/librbml/lib.rs:436

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:
I'm not the first one to see this one (#33733, #33015 -promise I'm not drunk tho heh) while building a brand new project with a single dependency:

```
[dependencies]
"synth" = "*"
```
